{"word":"G2126 - εὐλαβής - eulabḗs - yoo-lab-ace' - Devout","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐλαβής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eulabḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-lab-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Devout</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பக்தியுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. taking hold well, carefully and surely; cautious"},{"paragraph":"2. reverencing God, pious, religious, devout"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983 - λαμβάνω - lambánō - lam-ban'-o/2983\">G2983</a>; <i>taking well</i> (<i>carefully</i>), that is, <i>circumspect</i> (religiously, <i>pious</i>): - devout.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2125/2125\">G2125</a>, <a href=\"#/G2126/2126\">G2126</a>"}]}